{"type": "article", "id": 25669, "title": "ZARA给你推荐一周职场穿搭，以及，Porter男装值得一看｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-04-19T10:42:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 26418, "name": "古铜色"}, {"id": 26419, "name": "精油"}, {"id": 4288, "name": "假货"}, {"id": 26420, "name": "海关查扣"}, {"id": 1984, "name": "通勤"}, {"id": 1395, "name": "婚纱"}, {"id": 1802, "name": "Zara"}, {"id": 23649, "name": "NARS"}, {"id": 3120, "name": "Levi's"}, {"id": 26421, "name": "Urban Decay"}, {"id": 26422, "name": "Vogue Paris"}, {"id": 26423, "name": "New Avon"}, {"id": 6459, "name": "雅芳"}, {"id": 20048, "name": "Nordstrom"}, {"id": 26424, "name": "巴黎欧莱雅"}, {"id": 111, "name": "迪士尼"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 141, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021357230BulKwIAEJWVfkaY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/loreal-sales-rise-1-8-in-q1-10413015/\"><b>欧莱雅一季度销售额上涨 1.8%</b></a>｜美妆巨头公司巴黎欧莱雅日前发布最新财报，依靠消费品部门和在拉丁美州的积极市场表现、以及亚洲市场销售表现的缓和，截至 3 月 31 日的三个月内（一季度）收益上涨了 1.8% 至 65 亿欧元（约合 72.3 亿美元），略胜预期。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/department-stores/nordstrom-plans-350-400-job-cuts-10413425/\"><b>Nordstrom 百货将裁员 400 人</b></a>｜二月，总部位于西雅图的 Nordstrom 百货曾宣誓今年要在商业模式上做出巨大变革，而这周一，Nordstrom 百货宣布最新的计划是可能在二季度结束前，在企业总部及区域支持团队内裁员 350-400 人，目前全世界的雇员达到 70000 人。总裁 Blake Nordstrom 表示：“（裁员计划）改变运行模式以适应不断升级的顾客预期，确保每人都在最佳的位置以响应当今的商业环境和满足长期增长计划。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/people/new-avon-named-j-scott-white-ceo-cerberus-north-america-direct-selling-beauty-10412902/\"><b>New Avon 任命新 CEO</b></a>｜New Avon 近日宣布由 J. Scott White 担任首席执行官由雅芳北美业务组成的 New Avon，是私募股权基金公司 Cerberus Capital Management 与雅芳达成协议的产物，Cerberus 将向雅芳注资 4.35 亿美元，剥离出其北美业务，并通过额外投资 1.7 亿美元，将 New Avon 扶持成独立的公司。White 将在 4 月 25 日上任，此前他在雅培公司担任国际总裁，掌管 40 亿的营养贸易，在雅培任职的 10 年之前，他在宝洁公司有 15 年的工作经验，掌管一系列女性和健康品牌。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/vogue-paris-launches-first-model-competition-dior-img-10412877/\"><b>巴黎 Vogue 将举办模特大赛</b></a>｜巴黎版 Vogue 将首次举行模特大赛，合作方包括 Dior 美妆以及 IMG 模特经纪公司，要求候选人年龄必须在 16-25 岁之间，高于 5.6 英尺（约 1.67cm）且居住在法国，将出现在五月、六七月 Vogue Paris 杂志上。Vogue Paris 主编 Emmanuelle Alt 为首的评审团将在 9 月 10 日决选，获胜者除了登上杂志外还将参与 Dior Beauté 的项目及与 IMG Models 签约。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">每天都发愁穿什么去上班？<a href=\"http://www.zara.com/hk/en/editorials/woman-monday-to-friday-c819514.html\">Zara 拍摄了周一到周五的职场穿搭建议</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135707rVJW6hilP3coAbGe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135707sfFNDB82k4mPegcJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213570817qoUN06I4yGMpXh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135708tiyR0fsLhglXJK6V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135709q3g5zTXV8FjU7PWx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135709EK4L6Tc3gnysACS1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">一向很仙的 <a href=\"http://forums.thefashionspot.com/f60/elie-saab-bridal-s-s-2017-a-283879.html\">Elie Saab， 2016 春夏系列</a>的写真出炉：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021357107zRMf5eXKlmDtiaE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135710Fp4y5TWSKtQACYJj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135711oZGRXlCmDQzFViO1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021357127zJcmfY5knovU6iG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135712FHtmuSvB60qagC18.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">《美少女战士》日本官方推出<a href=\"http://popbee.cn/accessories/watches/sailor-moon-20th-anniversary-watch/\"> 20 周年纪念手表</a>，有皮质和金属两种表带供选择。预计在五月中旬上市，售价在 39800 日元，不过全球只限量发售 5000 块哦。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135712qeHFwAx6vUS1BscT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"> 由藤原浩掌舵的包袋品牌  Head Porter 你肯定不陌生了，其实旗下还有 Head Porter Plus 这个男装品牌，这里是<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/head-porter-plus-2016-spring-summer-collection-3\">其春夏系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135713KQtDyzIF19fkGXHL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135713CZDJwYOt3FzcSbq6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135714RdcJ56ajVChItT4A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135715iRJa2DgoWB3GKx1n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135715StXNVR3oP41d5bOA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135716FTduK1XbihESa5Wg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135716k72DK6bqEY1fxywI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">如果你也喜欢古铜色系的妆容，那么可以看看 <a href=\"http://popbee.cn/beauty/make-up/nars-tahiti-bronze-collection/\">NARS 新推出的 Tahiti Bronze 系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135717dBx8Vc4mHgGEMsDj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135717MTvs0qodGHlzmbgJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135718HTAFclbo29tZXEwD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135718mkEojZXhsFtCR2zy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>彩妆品牌 <a href=\"http://www.refinery29.com/2016/04/107883/urban-decay-disney-alice-through-the-looking-glass-collection#slide\">Urban Decay 推出迪士尼合作系列彩妆</a>，5 月 1 日开始在官网有售：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135719ih9o0fNRMnWDdIEv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66605505\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135719RglXZTGzSQjrEaJC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/3/levi-2016-spring-summer-commuter-collection\">Levi's Commuter 2016 年春夏系列</a>，继续强调自行车通勤、舒适牛仔的概念：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135720bjiXJxt40U9B8H6g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135720mStfaO7xicneCUvs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135721VHfmb5e6yuvU2cAa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135721uVwQb8rGjpZLm0RW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135722UrLp80W4ZIldSEVD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135722fehy38wQOXAYsKHC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}